---
title: BeaconLink Runtime Deployment Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Workflow as Workflow Engine
    participant Planner as Deployment Planner
    participant Relay as Relay Network
    participant Agent as BeaconLink Agent
    participant Runtime as Runtime Manager
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter
    participant Platform as Runtime Platform
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant Events as Event Streaming Platform
    participant Audit as Audit Service

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Dispatch
    %% =====================================================

    Workflow->>Planner: Execute immutable deployment revision
    Planner-->>Workflow: Deployment execution plan

    Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch deployment task
    Relay->>Agent: Deliver deployment instruction

    %% =====================================================
    %% Agent Validation
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Agent: Verify deployment revision
    Agent->>Policy: Validate deployment policy
    Policy-->>Agent: Deployment authorized

    Agent->>Agent: Verify runtime availability
    Agent->>Runtime: Initialize deployment session

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Translation
    %% =====================================================

    Runtime->>Adapter: Translate desired state

    Note right of Adapter: Runtime-independent\nBeaconLink specification\nis translated into\nplatform-specific operations.

    Adapter->>Adapter: Resolve runtime capabilities
    Adapter->>Adapter: Build execution plan
    Adapter-->>Runtime: Runtime execution plan

    %% =====================================================
    %% Platform Preparation
    %% =====================================================

    Runtime->>Platform: Validate platform health
    Platform-->>Runtime: Platform ready

    Runtime->>Platform: Reserve required resources
    Platform-->>Runtime: Resources allocated

    Runtime->>Platform: Validate dependencies
    Platform-->>Runtime: Dependencies satisfied

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Execution
    %% =====================================================

    Runtime->>Platform: Apply deployment

    loop Deployment Operations

        Platform-->>Runtime: Operation progress

        Runtime->>Agent: Runtime status

        Agent->>Relay: Progress update

        Relay->>Workflow: Forward progress

        Workflow->>Events: Publish DeploymentProgress

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Verification
    %% =====================================================

    Platform-->>Runtime: Deployment finished

    Runtime->>Platform: Verify workload health

    Platform-->>Runtime: Health check results

    Runtime->>Platform: Validate desired state

    Platform-->>Runtime: State converged

    %% =====================================================
    %% Inventory Synchronization
    %% =====================================================

    Runtime->>Agent: Runtime successful

    Agent->>Inventory: Update workload inventory
    Agent->>Inventory: Update runtime metadata
    Inventory-->>Agent: Inventory synchronized

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Completion
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Workflow: Deployment completed

    Workflow->>Audit: Record deployment success

    Workflow->>Events: Publish RuntimeDeploymentCompleted

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Reconciliation
    %% =====================================================

    loop Continuous Reconciliation

        Agent->>Runtime: Verify runtime state

        Runtime->>Platform: Compare desired vs actual

        alt Drift Detected

            Platform-->>Runtime: Configuration drift

            Runtime-->>Agent: Reconciliation required

            Agent->>Workflow: Drift report

            Workflow->>Events: Publish DriftDetected

        else State Healthy

            Runtime-->>Agent: Runtime healthy

        end

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure Handling
    %% =====================================================

    alt Runtime Failure

        Platform-->>Runtime: Deployment error

        Runtime-->>Agent: Failure diagnostics

        Agent->>Workflow: Runtime deployment failed

        Workflow->>Audit: Record runtime failure

        Workflow->>Planner: Generate rollback plan

        Planner-->>Workflow: Rollback revision

        Workflow->>Relay: Dispatch rollback

    else Successful Deployment

        Note over Agent,Platform: Runtime successfully converged<br/>to the immutable desired state.<br/>Continuous reconciliation maintains correctness.

    end